item.p:
Prior to this patch, the following code would not
evaluate: X = key,(fun(#{X := value}) -> true
end)(#{X => value})

taglist.item:
The functions converting
	    from lists got a performance loss for very small lists,
	    and a performance gain for very large lists.

item.p:
 The specifications of io_lib:fread/2,3 have
	    been corrected. (Thanks to Chris King and Kostis Sagonas
	    for pinpointing the bug.)

qlc:info() can now handle port identifiers,
	    pids, references, and funs. (Thanks to Wojciech Kaczmare
	    for reporting this bug.)
